r />\n人地打扮多少少又話人mk．．．著到成隻雞咁<br />\n好喇好喇，到搵到個完美o既又話人ps<br />\n屌你老母！除左識話人做雞之外仲識d咩！<br />\n你班仆街根本連女都無得屌呀！<br />\n上高登就扮撚晒大少，乜春都唔屌<br />\n死翻去現實就見到舊肥豬肉都扯旗<br />\n成世人連女人都未摸過<br />\n慘情到要日日對住AV打飛機<br />\n晚晚係高登同d人妖娘娘調情<br />\n唔好講話比欣宜你地屌唔屌<br />\n我諗比個白韻琴你地d毒男都成班餓狗搶屎咁搶住屌呀白小姐呀！"},{"pid":"3511e7a6335382b1725e9205d6e460b63100a979","tid":147771,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T06:02:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hani靚好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我女神係冇人能及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a075e9a538be804248c577503299c8d334034999","tid":147771,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T06:03:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊撚個黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n靚女一個"},{"pid":"502585f20ff1a947bfa0e23a9c1b73cac4eab3f3","tid":147771,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T06:04:05.000Z","msg":"各花各眼<br />\n不嬲覺唔靚<br />\n如果同小鳩陽菜比我會揀陽菜"},{"pid":"6816a380579cebbc26fda973b976bd8333322c4e","tid":147771,"uid":2470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T06:04:38.000Z","msg":"塑化雞"},{"pid":"c4f7730819931827a0899ae08598f88dda9d3f69","tid":147771,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"惡到有人覺得樣衰都唔得<br />\n堀北真希綾瀨遙都有人覺得唔靚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8830449f514410bebc028c7a3f37a6509a7e04fb","tid":147771,"uid":9910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T06:10:01.000Z","msg":"臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87695dad3541f88ee6f78ee66121728f8fa85206","tid":147771,"uid":54015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T06:10:11.000Z","msg":"平時食咩女同評論靚唔靚咩事<br />\n係咪要識踢波先可以睇英超<br />\n食開model 先可以睇av?"},{"pid":"97cc79694d4baf05